{"tid":841500,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"五個月同五十年","createTime":"2018-09-29T14:39:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-29T14:51:00.000Z","uid":213460,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1818d8425ac0242e8f6eda35e12c41e1e61b4697","tid":841500,"uid":213460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T14:39:25.000Z","msg":"如果俾你揀，衣食無憂，想做乜都得，但得五個月命。同埋五十年命，但可能要憂柴憂米，你會點揀？(留低你嘅唸法啦)<br />\n我寧願煙花般璀璨五個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n細細品味生活各種滋味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d8c69d5bda9f32bc9f274d1b8cb34f06f833119","tid":841500,"uid":129043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T14:42:35.000Z","msg":"享受5個月同折磨50年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e0bd01a7330d229e30ebbba470d58aa846f51d6","tid":841500,"uid":213460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T14:51:00.000Z","msg":"有人話應該享受過程，咁依家俾五個月你隨便享受結果。仲會唔會有人會揀五十年拼搏同一個未知嘅結局？"}]}